Package: MixMatrix
Type: Package
Title: Classification with Matrix Variate Normal and t distributions
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2019-06-21
Authors@R: c(person(c("Geoffrey", "Thompson"),email="gzthompson@gmail.com",
          role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = '0000-0003-2436-8822')))
Description: Provides sampling and density functions for matrix
    variate normal, t, and inverted t distributions;  ML fitting for matrix
    variate normal and t distributions including some restrictions on the
    parameters; and linear and quadratic discriminant analysis for matrix
    variate normal and t distributions. 
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    stats, 
    CholWishart,
    Rcpp
